{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6240aba9d5","title":"关于无产阶级政党也要吐故纳新的谈话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0073cb3d0b","index":0,"year":1967,"month":11,"day":5,"articleId":"6240aba9d5"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"318138ea26","name":"重要党政机构及其衍变","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"e2305b9e63","name":"毛泽东","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a6880d6195","type":"title","text":"关于无产阶级政党也要吐故纳新的谈话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6240aba9d5"},{"id":"e05e725baa","type":"paragraph","text":"一个人有动脉、静脉，通过心脏进行血液循环，还要通过肺部进行呼吸，呼出二氧化碳，吸进新鲜氧气，这就是吐故纳新。一个无产阶级的党也要吐故纳新，才能朝气蓬勃。不清除废料，不吸收新鲜血液，党就没有朝气。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6240aba9d5"}],"page":{"id":"97bbcdb534","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"6240aba9d5","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}